title: Aidynn Cupido
text:
Aidynn Cupido (born 4 September 1996) is a South African <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player for the in the <a href="Pro14%20Rainbow%20Cup">Pro14 Rainbow Cup SA</a> and in the <a href="Currie%20Cup">Currie Cup</a>. His regular position is fly-half.
Cupido was named in the squad for the <a href="Pro14%20Rainbow%20Cup">Pro14 Rainbow Cup SA</a> competition, and was then named in the squad for the <a href="2021%20Currie%20Cup%20Premier%20Division">2021 Currie Cup Premier Division</a>. He made his debut for the Golden Lions in Round 1 of the <a href="2021%20Currie%20Cup%20Premier%20Division">2021 Currie Cup Premier Division</a> against the .
